2 HOUSE BILL 339
1 11–102.
2 This title applies only in Anne Arundel County.
3 11–204.
4 (b) (2) The Board shall employ:
5 (i) a full–time executive director whose annual salary shall be fixed
6 by the Board as in a general county classified salary schedule, within pay grade 17;
7 (ii) a full–time administrator whose annual salary shall be fixed by
8 the Board as in a general county classified salary schedule, within pay grade 16;
9 (iii) two full–time secretaries whose annual salaries shall be fixed by
10 the Board as in a general county classified salary schedule, within pay grade 13;
11 (iv) a full–time chief inspector whose annual salary shall be fixed by
12 the Board as in a general county classified salary schedule, within non–represented pay
13 schedule [NR–05] NR–15; and
14 (v) an attorney at an annual salary of $60,000.
15 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect July
16 1, 2026.
